      "title": "Deadline for 2023 Grade 01 admission applications extended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has extended the deadline for the applications for the admission of students to Grade 01 in government schools for the Year 2023.",
        "Accordingly, the new closing date for submitting applications will be the 01st of August 2022.",
        "The ministry said it received multiple requests from parents seeking a deadline extension due to the crisis situation in the country."
      ],
